{
  "chapter": 24,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十四回\"悲欢离合\"讲述了丁灵琳与葛病的婚礼悲剧。丁灵琳在花烛前扶起葛病，表示要嫁给他，但葛病话未说完便倒地身亡。丁灵琳悲痛欲绝，点燃了鸿宾客栈。叶开酒醉醒来，发现鸿宾客栈已成废墟，幸遇崔玉真。崔玉真告诉他，鸿宾客栈昨夜发生惨案，喜堂内尸横遍地，黄衣人（金钱帮）搬走了所有尸体。丁灵琳与葛病返回时，遭遇孤峰天王（布达拉），葛病为救丁灵琳被其一掌击毙。叶开得知真相后，决定先找凶手，再找孤峰天王。崔玉真因叶开心中有丁灵琳而心碎离去，约定将来为他熬粥。本章展现了悲欢离合的主题，丁灵琳的善良、葛病的牺牲、叶开的深情、崔玉真的痴心，交织成一段凄美的江湖情缘。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ge_bing",
      "text": "现在我就要嫁给你，做你的妻子，终生依靠你，所以你一定要活下去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ge_bing",
      "text": "这里虽然没有喜官，但我们却一样还是可以拜天地，只要我们两个人愿意，有没有别人做见证都一样。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ge_bing",
      "speaker_name": "葛病",
      "listener": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "text": "我这一生中，一直都在盼望能有这么样一天……我本来以为我已永远不会有这么样一天了；可是现在……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叶开你说过，只要等一切事解决，你就会来找我，现在什么事都完了，你为什么还不来？……为什么子……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路人甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里是什么时候起火的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路人乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路人丙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "昨天夜里我在赌叶子牌，就算天塌下来，我也不会知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路人丁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "听说昨天晚上有人在这里做喜事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路人戊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好像是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路人己",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那些来喝喜酒的人，怎么连一个都不在？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路人庚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路人辛",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那对新人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路人壬",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路人癸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里的老掌柜呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路人子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路人丑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我别的事都不奇怪，只奇怪那对新人居然也不在这洞房里，连老掌柜都不见了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路人寅",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道这里昨天晚上出了狐仙？出了鬼？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "早。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "早。粥已熬好了，你就躺在床上吃？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你昨天晚上一定醉得很厉害。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 377
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "醉得简直就像是条死狗。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我若是你，我也要醉的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你知道昨天晚上的事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "本来我还不知道。那天早上我被伊夜哭逼着回到玉箫那里去，他就……就再也不许我出来。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我本来这一辈子已完了，我实在想不到那恶魔也有死在别人手里的一天。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "玉箫一死，你就到这里来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "姐妹们一听到他的死讯，就像是刚飞出笼子的鸟，都恨不得飞得远远的，每个人分了他一点东西，不到一个时辰就全都走了，只有我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我一个人在这屋子里待了一整天，既不想出去，也睡不着。其实我也知道你是绝不会再回到这里来的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "直到昨天早上，我听到了外面的爆竹声，才想起已经是大年初一。我不想一个人再闷在屋子里，又饿得发慌了，忍不住想到外面去走走，可是我想不到刚出去，就听见个很可怕的消息。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "什么消息？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我听说丁姑娘要成亲了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "这消息并不可怕。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "可是……那时候我还以为她……她要好的人是你。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我听见丁姑娘要嫁的人，是个受了伤的人，我更以为他就是你。那时我心里虽然难受，却又希望能在喜筵上再见你一次，所以我就买了份礼，送到鸿宾客栈去。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "可是到了晚上，我又不敢去喝喜酒了。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你不敢？你怕什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我……我忽然又怕见到你。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "那时你还不知道新郎倌并不是我了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我还不知道。所以我又把自己关在这屋子里，一个人买了点酒，躲在这里喝，我想，我也可以算是在喝你们的喜酒了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "我若知道你在这里，我一定来陪你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我喝了一点酒后，又忍不住想去看看你了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你去了没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我迟疑了很久，反反复复的拿不定主意，我既怕看见你们后会受不了，可是就这么样永不相见，我也不甘心。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "到最后我终于拿定主意。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "什么主意？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我就算不去喝你们的喜酒，也得在外面偷偷的看你一眼。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "昨天是大年初一，到了晚上，街上几乎连一个人都没有，我在街上逛了很久，才鼓起勇气，从客栈后面溜了进去，一进去我就知道不对了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 496,
      "line_end": 498
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "什么地方不对？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 500,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "那么大的客栈里，竟连一点声音都没有，非但一点也不像有人在办喜事，就是办丧事的人家，都没有那么静。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "我知道去喝喜酒的人不少，怎么会连一点声音都没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 506,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我找到了办喜事的那个大厅，从窗口往里面一看……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 510,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你看见了什么人？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 514,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我……我……我只看见喜堂里到处全是血，全是死人，竟连一个活着的都没有。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 519
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "当时我还以为你也在里面，所以我立刻就不顾一切，冲了进去。直到那时，我才知道丁姑娘要嫁的人并不是你。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 527
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你……你看见了那个新郎倌？他也死了？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他死得很惨。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "丁灵琳呢了她是不是也……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 536,
      "line_end": 537
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "她没有死，当时她根本不在那喜堂里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "当时我虽然又吃惊，又害怕，可是看见你不在里面，我总算松了口气。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你有没有看见四个黄衣人的尸体？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我没有注意别人，也不敢仔细去看。那些尸体里面，好像是有几个穿着黄衣服的人。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 552,
      "line_end": 553
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "他们若是也死了，凶手会是谁呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 556
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我也想不透，世上怎会有这么心狠手辣的人，当时我只想赶快离开那地方，谁知我刚想走的时候，忽然听见外面有夜行人的衣袂带风声。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 558,
      "line_end": 559
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "因为那地方实在太静，所以我听得很清楚，来的人非但身法都很快，而且还不止一个人。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 562,
      "line_end": 563
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "莫非是那些凶手又回来了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "当时我也这么想，所以吓得连走都不敢走了，更不敢留在那里，让他们看见，幸好我还有点武功，情急之下，武功好像反而比平时好了些，居然一跳就跳起来很高。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 569
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你是不是跳上了大厅里的那根横梁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 572,
      "line_end": 572
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我躲在上面，连气都不敢喘，却又忍不住想往下面看看。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 575
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你看见了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我看见了几个穿着黄衣服的人，从外面一窜进来，立刻就将地上的死人，一个个抛出了窗外，窗外好像有人在用东西接着，不到片刻，屋子里的死人居然全都被他们搬空了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 581
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你看清楚他们身上穿的是黄衣服？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 584,
      "line_end": 584
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我看得很清楚，因为他们的衣服黄得很特别，在灯光下看起来，就好像有金光在闪动着一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 586,
      "line_end": 588
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "果然是他们下的毒手。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 590,
      "line_end": 590
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "可是我并没有看见他们杀人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 592,
      "line_end": 592
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "人若不是他们杀的，他们为什么要替别人收尸？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 594
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他们杀了人后，难道还想毁尸灭迹？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 596,
      "line_end": 596
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "杀人灭口，毁尸灭迹，本就是金钱帮的一贯作风。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 598,
      "line_end": 598
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "金钱帮？……金钱帮又是些什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "他们不是人。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 602,
      "line_end": 602
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "后来我又看见了丁姑娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 604,
      "line_end": 606
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你在哪里看见她的？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 608,
      "line_end": 608
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "就在那里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 610,
      "line_end": 610
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "她又回去了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 612,
      "line_end": 612
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "那些黄衣人把尸体搬空之后，她就去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 614,
      "line_end": 614
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "那时你还没有走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 616,
      "line_end": 616
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "那时候我整个人都已吓得发软，在大梁上待了半天，刚喘过一口气，他们就来了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 618,
      "line_end": 619
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "他们？她不是一个人去的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 622
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "去的有两个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "还有个人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 626,
      "line_end": 626
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "是个奇形怪状的老头子，半夜里手里还拿着把雨伞。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 628,
      "line_end": 628
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "是葛病。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 630,
      "line_end": 630
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你认得他。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 632,
      "line_end": 632
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "不但认得，而且还是老朋友。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 634,
      "line_end": 634
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "那么现在你的老朋友就又少了一个。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 637
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "他也死了子",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 640,
      "line_end": 640
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "死得也很惨。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 642,
      "line_end": 642
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "是谁杀了他？是谁下的毒手？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 644,
      "line_end": 644
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他们看见尸身被搬空，也觉得很意外，可是他们并没有停留，也没有发现梁上还有别人在。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 646,
      "line_end": 648
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "后来呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 650,
      "line_end": 650
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他们一走，我就溜了下去，忽然听到外面有人在吹笛子，他们听见了这笛声，也赶了回来，在院子里看了看，就越墙而出。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 652,
      "line_end": 653
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 656,
      "line_end": 656
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我看他们的神情很慌张，也不禁觉得有点好奇。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 658
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "所以你也跟了过去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 660,
      "line_end": 660
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我没有跟过去，只不过躲在墙头往外面看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 662,
      "line_end": 662
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你又看见了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 664,
      "line_end": 664
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "外面一棵树上，好像挂着盏灯笼，下面还站着个人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 666,
      "line_end": 666
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 668,
      "line_end": 668
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我隔得太远，根本看不清楚，幸好当时四下一点声音都没有，所以他们说话的声音，我倒全都听见了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 671
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "他们说了些什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 674,
      "line_end": 674
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "丁姑娘过去后，好像惊叫了一声，然后就问那个人，是不是布……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 676,
      "line_end": 677
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "布达拉？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 678,
      "line_end": 678
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "不错，布达拉，丁姑娘说的就是这三个字。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 681
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "那个人怎么说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 684,
      "line_end": 684
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他承认了，还说自己是座很高的山峰。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 686,
      "line_end": 686
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "孤峰天王？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 688,
      "line_end": 688
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "后来我才知道，那个人就是魔教中的四大天王之一。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 690,
      "line_end": 690
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "葛病就是死在他手里的？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 692,
      "line_end": 692
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "葛老先生是为了救丁姑娘，才被他掌力所伤，可是他也中了葛老先生的暗器，我听葛老先生告诉丁姑娘，那是种很厉害的暗器。可是他的掌力更可怕，葛老先生只被他轻轻拍了一掌，就已无救了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 694,
      "line_end": 699
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "可是我亲眼看见葛老先生倒下去的，就倒在第一个新郎倌倒下去的地方。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 708,
      "line_end": 710
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "我知道她一定会这么样做的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 720,
      "line_end": 720
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你不怪她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 722,
      "line_end": 722
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你若是她，我相信你一定也会这么样做的，因为你们都是心地善良的女孩子，你们都宁愿牺牲自己，也不忍看着别人受苦。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 724,
      "line_end": 725
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "只可惜我不是她，我……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 732,
      "line_end": 733
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你走的时候，她还留在火窟里？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 734,
      "line_end": 734
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "但是你可以放心，她现在一定还好好的活着。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 738,
      "line_end": 739
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "因为火窟里并没有她的尸骨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 742,
      "line_end": 742
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "也因为她是个善良的女孩子，吉人自有天相，我相信你们很快就会再见的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 744,
      "line_end": 745
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "不管怎么样，现在我总算已确定了两件事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 752,
      "line_end": 753
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "不管那布拉达天王是什么人，现在他一定已受了重伤，我已不难找到他。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 758,
      "line_end": 759
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你一定要去找他？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 762,
      "line_end": 762
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "可是我还要先去找另外一个人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 764,
      "line_end": 764
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "找谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 766,
      "line_end": 766
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "去找那杀人的凶手。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 768,
      "line_end": 768
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你……你现在就要去？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 770,
      "line_end": 771
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "我现在就要去，你……你可以在这里等我，我会回来的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 772,
      "line_end": 773
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你用不着回来了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 778,
      "line_end": 779
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 782,
      "line_end": 782
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "因为我……我不会在这里等你的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 784,
      "line_end": 784
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 788,
      "line_end": 788
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "因为我不是她，我……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 790,
      "line_end": 791
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你要到哪里去？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 794,
      "line_end": 794
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我有很多地方可去，我也早就想到处去看看，到处去走走，将来……我说不定会找个老实的男人，嫁给他，替他生很多很多儿子，也说不定会开个小酒店，做一个当炉卖酒的老板娘……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 796,
      "line_end": 797
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "text": "到那时我一定会到你的酒店里去大醉一场。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 800,
      "line_end": 800
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "崔玉真",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "到那时候我一定会替你再熬一锅鸡粥，有燕窝的鸡粥。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 24,
      "line_start": 804,
      "line_end": 805
    }
